Preheat oven to 350°F with rack in upper third. Butter a 2-quart shallow baking dish. Whisk together all ingredients with 1 1/2 teaspoons salt and 1 teaspoon pepper in a large bowl. Transfer to baking dish. Bake until pudding is set, 1 to 1 1/4 hours. Cool 10 minutes before serving. Josmeyer Les Folastries
